text: Marian Leszczyński was a rower from Poland. Leszczyński competed at the 1964 Summer Olympics. He was born on 8 December 1936 and died on 31 December 2020.Marian Leszczyński == References == Category:1936 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Polish rowers Category:Olympians for Poland
